3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the design of a distributed MIMO transceiver, which involves control and system design aspects. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper mentions the possibility of the distributed MIMO transceiver serving different standards or services, which could include multimedia applications.
